{"tid":25880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丟人現眼！  日本駐港總領事館發通告　呼籲居港國民提防拐子佬","createTime":"2016-12-06T11:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T14:16:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2efe7797ba823a62407a30f908c36d1cb990aa2d","tid":25880,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201612/20161205JP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201612%2F20161205JP.jpg&h=933d7abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕跡香港多年，幾成都市傳說的「拐子佬」個案近年屢傳發生，甚至揚威海外。今日（12月5日）日本駐香港總領事館經官方網站及電郵發出通告，提醒居港日本人注意近日香港發生的多宗企圖拐帶案。 <br />\n<br />\n該通告引述近日兩宗拐子佬疑雲，包括啟思幼稚園九龍塘分校於11月30日傳出有陌生男子試圖在九龍塘港鐵站外的士站拖走一名學童事敗；以及香港仔天主教聖伯多祿幼稚園12月2日發生疑有陌生男子強抱小朋友個案。兩幼稚園校方已先後向家長發出通告，提醒注意子女人身安全。 <br />\n<br />\n日本駐香港總領事館呼籲居港國民注意上述誘拐事件，又提醒家長需教育兒童分辨熟人與陌生人、如陌生人有所行動需大聲呼救、有需要可隨身攜帶兒童用防狼警報器、如乘坐校巴亦需安排照顧者親自接送、勿讓兒童單獨外出、以及外出時拖緊兒童，勿讓兒童遠離視線範圍。 <br />\n<br />\n日本神戶市上月就發生中國大媽拐帶女童案，一名居日中國籍女子被控在超級市場拐走一名4歲女童。婦人被捕後竟向警方供稱「女童太可愛想帶她回家。不是誘拐」，社會嘩然，難怪對拐帶案人心惶惶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-05-2016/34325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-05-2016%2F34325&d=594jwF06iYRaoK%2BpvQI4GEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ad3c896b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-05-2016/34325</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk.emb-japan.go.jp/jp/docs/ryoji_anzen_20161205.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk.emb-japan.go.jp%2Fjp%2Fdocs%2Fryoji_anzen_20161205.pdf&d=594jwF06iYRaoK%2BpvQI4GEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=534cdb87\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk.emb-japan.go.jp/jp/docs/ryoji_anzen_20161205.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c97415279a7acfaa433cd0891c79b005062acdd2","tid":25880,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8323909266499657bf90a1d74617c84176ccc779","tid":25880,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b503bccde7ac97d045d066e44f557173e3259a","tid":25880,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"日本鍾於識分香港同支那分別<br />\n支那人 我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d487d545bbadd8ee1703acb594df593c78ea4ceb","tid":25880,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d53402bcfe38df1f9a06b5e183a42e24d986984","tid":25880,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9c56f557a266895d24eb592119b1a51b21cebe","tid":25880,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff03272f45ece4dca258073f37018465d6645e8","tid":25880,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"乜撚丟人現眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦改人個topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3a3c3e41beeed7e984897cf7a28a6bac2e02a0","tid":25880,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.makeagif.com/media/9-01-2015/iZoIo4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F9-01-2015%2FiZoIo4.gif&h=f0c8fc9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c035c74aa3271ac5ee3a24ea8308c7f8f129a28","tid":258